\">去「證明」自己快樂後先得到快樂</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢度唔只係講金錢上消費，而係我地行為習慣，情緒感覺都因此改變。"},{"pid":"9d01fdaf154f00ba6eb1a1062f7a13bbbd7e5d8e","tid":2168837,"uid":23198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57430928986df605911c34b6287aa3857130425c","tid":2168837,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T04:54:21.000Z","msg":"一支大麻，即刻脫離被控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:03:50.000Z","msg":"都得，但依加情況係我地大腦被商家/社會入侵。<br />\n<br />\n麻醉自己但佢地仍然係度。"},{"pid":"56b4dc2c80abea9e9d2ccb5aaaeeb5934a0ad0c1","tid":2168837,"uid":46933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:06:32.000Z","msg":"社會既一切都會令人迷失而痛苦"},{"pid":"2651e5a8e81a245f35ff26ecb0f0c6fd7aff9d88","tid":2168837,"uid":296028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:06:47.000Z","msg":"自己買人工鑽石去整個指環，得晒"},{"pid":"e3f6f05d53fc6d309ca358a461925aa1704c83a8","tid":2168837,"uid":23198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad360c5d307a3c92b88f43266b0a69c79df4e6bb","tid":2168837,"uid":201604,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T04:52:12.000Z","msg":"冇獨立思考既人咪係"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:07:23.000Z","msg":"我地可以唔跟<br />\n但如果大腦對呢樣野有反應既話其實都已經出左問題<br />\n<br />\n就算唔跟都已經被入侵左情緒系統<br />\n從而潛移默化改變我地行為"},{"pid":"e8c7fc0c1fecd1b797f5528b7571ba59df8a9f9c","tid":2168837,"uid":23198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"56b4dc2c80abea9e9d2ccb5aaaeeb5934a0ad0c1","tid":2168837,"uid":46933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:06:32.000Z","msg":"社會既一切都會令人迷失而痛苦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:22:13.000Z","msg":"社會體制只係為左社會而服務<br />\n<br />\n如果人活著係為左得到快樂既話<br />\n社會定立左好多條條框框令我地滿足其他人<br />\n<br />\n社會本身應該為人類平穩而服務，係一個共生關係。<br />\n但被商家/有心人利用要人為社會服務<br />\n<br />\n本身好簡單就得到既野<br />\n佢會同你講要做到ABCDE先會得到果樣野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自我價值     身份認同都係咁<br />\n<br />\n就例如，你本身係個善良既人，<br />\n睇呢個世界都係好美好，唔會傷害其他人。<br />\n但社會制約同你講<br />\n你一定要守佢既規條先係一個善良既人。<br />\n<br />\n規條道德本身應該係一個引導人向真實善美既指引<br />\n但唔應該變成「證明自己」既工具"},{"pid":"7f11bfcc15359d6091f6a5908dcb9e30412a6920","tid":2168837,"uid":71197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:52:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">其實社會上所有嘢都係</span>"},{"pid":"847f51c8e08e88a652e9f895cb2e4f1174411389","tid":2168837,"uid":71197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e39f7603fbf92ea95b30bc1f34cf8a9edf32e4d","tid":2168837,"uid":71197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e1d586c7712de05b595eff26eb7268305b1cf9","tid":2168837,"uid":23198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:43:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c72c6e4bb049b01a1d9ab3cbc40801cfb1b51bf9","tid":2168837,"uid":15960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T15:50:26.000Z","msg":"諗諗吓 整容興起都係..<br />\n乜嘢黃金比例 完美指標"},{"pid":"f652a443fd210d33f68af163442331fd1ff952da","tid":2168837,"uid":245711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T15:51:54.000Z","msg":"04158964"},{"pid":"91413e057456cf5e11adb969fb17dfeb8301f7fa","tid":2168837,"uid":93714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:55:06.000Z","msg":"樓主more<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d7afe623fa412858c3db19124ff0cebeea1b35","tid":2168837,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:59:15.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭西五顏六色"},{"pid":"e74ca7b0040ee6e0ebd4a9a0606a41bee2b95df8","tid":2168837,"uid":258230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3f6f05d53fc6d309ca358a461925aa1704c83a8","tid":2168837,"uid":23